            "title": "盤中速報 - 竑騰(7751)大漲8.48%，報479.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>竑騰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7751:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7751\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7751-TW</a>)28日13:10股價上漲37.5元，報479.5元，漲幅8.48%，成交203張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>竑騰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7751:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7751\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7751-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為半導體自動化生產及光學檢測設備。治具、零件及維修收入。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌3.91%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.09%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-55 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-53 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-2 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
